BUT HEARTBREAK IS NOT SOMETHING TO BE AVOIDED.

00:16:42.850 --> 00:16:47.820
HEARTBREAK IS THE GREATEST CLUE OF OUR LIVES, RIGHT,

00:16:47.820 --> 00:16:48.990
BECAUSE WHAT BREAKS YOUR HEART

