00:16:55.160 --> 00:16:56.860
AND FOR YOU, IT'S ANIMAL CRUELTY.

00:16:56.860 --> 00:16:59.070
AND WHAT HAPPENS WHEN YOU FIND THAT THING

00:16:59.070 --> 00:17:01.600
THAT BREAKS YOUR HEART OPEN AND MAKES YOU --

00:17:01.600 --> 00:17:03.740
MAKES IT HARD TO BREATHE,

00:17:03.740 --> 00:17:05.610
AND YOU DON'T "EASY" BUTTON YOUR WAY OUT

00:17:05.610 --> 00:17:07.840
BUT YOU LET IT BE YOUR PROFESSOR,

00:17:07.840 --> 00:17:09.480
IT GUIDES YOU TOWARDS THE PEOPLE

00:17:09.480 --> 00:17:11.910
WHO ARE DOING THAT WORLD-HEALING WORK

00:17:11.910 --> 00:17:14.680
IN THE WORLD, RIGHT?

00:17:14.680 --> 00:17:16.350
AND THERE YOU FIND YOUR PURPOSE,

00:17:16.350 --> 00:17:19.920
AND THEN THE BONUS IS, THAT THERE YOU FIND YOUR TRIBE.

00:17:19.920 --> 00:17:22.390
BECAUSE THERE'S NO BOND GREATER THAN THE BOND THAT HAPPENS

00:17:22.390 --> 00:17:28.160
BETWEEN PEOPLE DOING THE SAME WORLD-HEALING WORK TOGETHER.

00:17:28.160 --> 00:17:31.370
YOU GUYS AND GIRLS AND WOMEN,

00:17:31.370 --> 00:17:33.530
IF WE STOPPED FEARING OUR PAIN,

00:17:33.530 --> 00:17:36.740
WE WOULD HEAL OUR NATION, OKAY?

00:17:36.740 --> 00:17:40.880
WE ARE IN A SWEATY-ASS YOGA CLASS RIGHT NOW...

