00:17:47.810 --> 00:17:49.350
BECAUSE EVERYTHING WE NEED

00:17:49.350 --> 00:17:51.690
TO BECOME THE COUNTRY WE WERE MEANT TO BE,

00:17:51.690 --> 00:17:54.750
TO BECOME GREAT FOR THE FIRST TIME

00:17:54.750 --> 00:17:57.160
FOR ALL OF US, RIGHT,

00:17:57.160 --> 00:17:59.390
IS INSIDE THE HOT LONELINESS

00:17:59.390 --> 00:18:01.560
OF OUR COLLECTIVE PAIN RIGHT NOW.

00:18:01.560 --> 00:18:02.730
OKAY?

