..."LIFE IS PAIN, HIGHNESS,

00:21:32.440 --> 00:21:34.040
AND ANYONE WHO TELLS YOU DIFFERENTLY

00:21:34.040 --> 00:21:36.810
IS SELLING YOU SOMETHING."

